{"tid":53744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門立法會議員高天賜 2名兒子涉販毒被","createTime":"2016-12-25T02:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T07:44:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7365338202de30364b9758c4f71d88c08e8f2b","tid":53744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161224/56089933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161224%2F56089933&d=Izm59kg6lzzydDMux2p49wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d6c215e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161224%2F56089933&h=a896d85b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161224/56089933</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門司警日前搗破一宗跨境販毒案，撿獲一公斤大麻花，拘捕2名澳門集團主腦，澳門傳媒報道兩名疑犯是澳門立法會議員高天賜的兒子。 <br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，澳門司警接報有本地販毒組織與跨境販毒集團合作販賣毒品，經深入調查後，本月15日於中區拘捕提取毒品的高氏兄弟，撿獲4包共值1公斤的大麻花，其後再拘捕一名姓黃男子。警方初步調查顯示，被捕高氏兄弟分別31及27歲，是販毒集團主腦，姓黃疑犯則是下線拆家。 <br />\n<br />\n其後有消息盛傳高氏兄弟是立法會議員高天賜的一對兒子，高以短訊回覆當地傳媒，承認自己平常沒有時間關心2個兒子，對2人被捕感到非常痛心，妻子已經由外國回到澳門，連日來都以淚洗面。"},{"pid":"045751090c6d6ed18c4fdd655d7f67b9aac109f9","tid":53744,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:54:55.000Z","msg":"見FB D澳門仔話,單野有政治陰毛<br />\n話個個立法會議員都有黑材料,唔聽話就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618cc5900543350898e2433edcb662b19c75b270","tid":53744,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見FB D澳門仔話,單野有政治陰毛<br />\n話個個立法會議員都有黑材料,唔聽話就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑乜鳩材料<br />\n叫開痛腳/把柄"},{"pid":"567e248c1de3651881c553195f0fd36965565703","tid":53744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201